m/somali/43854862|title=Berbera oo laga furay maktabadii ugu horraysay ee ay yeelato mudo dheer|website=BBC|language=so|access-date=22 April 2018}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://wargeyskadawan.com/2019/07/19/maktabada-akhriska-ee-magaaladda-berbera-oo-buugaag-gaadhsiisay-magaalooyinka-dacar-budhuq-iyo-abdaal|title=Maktabada Akhriska Ee Magaaladda Berbera Oo Buugaag Gaadhsiisay Magaalooyinka Dacar Budhuq Iyo Abdaal|website=Wargeyska Dawan|date=19 July 2019|access-date=10 March 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.somtribune.com/2017/03/11/berbera-mayor-lauds-dahabshiil-boost-city-library/?pr=75450&lang=en|title=Berbera Mayor lauds Dahabshiil boost to city library|website=Som Tribune|date=11 March 2017|access-date=10 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n==See also==\n{{Portal|somaliland|library}}\n* [[National Library of Somaliland]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [https://twitter.com/berberapublic?lang=en Berbera Public Library on Twitter]\n\n{{coord missing|Somalia}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Government of Somaliland]]\n[[Category:National libraries|Somaliland]]\n[[Category:World Digital Library partners]]\n[[Category:Libraries in Somalia]]\n\n\n{{somaliland-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Library in Somaliland}}\n{{Infobox building\n| name                = Berbera Public Library\n| native_name         = Maktabadda Dadweynaha ee Berbera\n| former_names        = \n| alternate_names     = \n| image               = Berbera Public Library.jpg\n| caption             = The exterior of Berbera Public Library\n| map_type            = \n| altitude            = \n| building_type       = \n| architectural_style = \n| structural_system   = \n| cost                = \n| ren_cost            = \n| location            = [[Berbera, Somaliland]]\n| address             = \n| client              = \n| owner               = [[Berbera|Berbera County Council]]\n| current_tenants     = \n| landlord            = \n| coordinates         = \n| sta